The question arises by itself: Collserola, Park or Berg?
The call for tenders is not only from an organizational point of view, but also in view of a reflection on the city the topic of discussion in the mouth of all architects from Barcelona.
It is almost a recurring topic, which two members of this old caste, who meet in the elevator, can fall back on.
